---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Level 4: Authority & Channels | Waseem's SEO Guide">
  <nav class="breadcrumbs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
    <ol>
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/level3">Level 3</a></li>
      <li aria-current="page">Level 4: Authority & Channels</li>
    </ol>
  </nav>

  <header>
    <span class="badge">LEVEL 4</span>
    <h1>🌐 Authority & Channels</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Practice-First Learning: Build Your Digital Authority Across Channels</p>
    <div class="reading-time-badge">⏱️ ~60 min read</div>
  </header>

  <section class="intro-section">
    <h2>What You'll Learn</h2>
    <p>Level 4 focuses on building authority across multiple channels - from backlinks to reviews, from local SEO to video optimization.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>📚 Modules Covered</h2>
    <ul class="topics-list">
      <li>✓ 4.1: Off-Page SEO Fundamentals</li>
      <li>✓ 4.2: Local SEO + Google Business Profile</li>
      <li>✓ 4.3: Reviews & Reputation Management</li>
      <li>✓ 4.4: Video SEO (VEO)</li>
      <li>✓ 4.5: Social Search Optimization</li>
      <li>✓ 4.6: Capstone Project</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <div class="content-coming-soon">
    <p>🚧 Full content coming soon! This is a preview of the Astro-based structure.</p>
    <p>In the meantime, you can view the <a href="/level1">Level 1 content</a> for a complete example.</p>
  </div>

  <nav class="level-nav">
    <a href="/level3" class="nav-btn">← Level 3: Advanced GEO</a>
    <a href="/" class="nav-btn">🏠 Back to Home</a>
  </nav>
</Layout>

<style>
  .breadcrumbs ol {
    display: flex;
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .breadcrumbs a {
    color: #667eea;
  }

  header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .badge {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe 0%, #4facfe 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 8px 20px;
    border-radius: 25px;
  }

  .topics-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }
  .topics-list li {
    padding: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .content-coming-soon {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff3e0 0%, #ffe0b2 100%);
    border-radius: 15px;
    margin: 40px 0;
  }

  .level-nav {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .level-nav .nav-btn {
    padding: 12px 24px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4facfe 0%, #4facfe 100%);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
</style>
